'''隕石學'''是一門涉及[[隕石|隕石]]和其它地球外物質，能讓我們更進一步了解[[太陽系|太陽系]]的歷史和其起源的科學<ref>{{cite encyclopedia |date=19 December 2012 |title=meteoritics, n. |encyclopedia=OED Online |publisher=Oxford University Press |location= |id= |url=http://www.oed.com/view/Entry/117479 |access-date=2014-11-30 |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414105105/https://www.oed.com/start?authRejection=true&url=%2Fview%2FEntry%2F117479 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>A rarely used synonym is ''Astrolithology'': {{cite journal|last=Leonard|first=Frederick C.|title=Introducing meteoritics: The Journal of the Meteoritical Society and the Institute of Meteoritics of the University of New Mexico|journal=Meteoritics|year=1953|volume=1|issue=1|pages=1–4|doi=10.1111/j.1945-5100.1953.tb01299.x}}</ref>。專門研究隕石的人稱為'''隕石學家'''<ref>{{cite encyclopedia |date=19 December 2012 |title=meteoriticist, n. |encyclopedia=OED Online |publisher=Oxford University Press |location= |id= |url=http://www.oed.com/view/Entry/236863 |access-date=2014-11-30 |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414071724/https://www.oed.com/start;jsessionid=6B5CB9FA4910167D0840B8D0A5ABE25B?authRejection=true&url=%2Fview%2FEntry%2F236863 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 研究的歷史 ==
{{Incomplete|章節|date=December 2012}}

在[[萊格爾_(隕石)|萊格爾隕石]]的研究報告出來之前，人們相信隕石是一種異端邪說，那些聲稱看到隕石從天而降的人是在說謊。

在1960年，[[約翰·雷諾_(物理學家)|約翰·雷諾]]發現一些隕石有過量的[[氙|<sup>129</sup>氙]]，是存在於太陽星雲中的[[碘|<sup>129</sup>碘]]衰變的結果<ref name="Reynolds 1960">{{cite journal|last=Reynolds|first=J.|title=Isotopic Composition of Primordial Xenon|journal=Physical Review Letters|date=31 March 1960|volume=4|issue=7|pages=351–354|doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.4.351|bibcode = 1960PhRvL...4..351R }}</ref>。

== 研究的方法 ==
=== 礦物學 ===
有些礦物的存在與否，是經過某些物理或化學過程的指標。母體受到的撞擊會記錄在撞擊角礫岩和高壓礦物的相位（例如[[柯石英|柯石英]]、[[akimotoite|akimotoite]]、[[鎂鐵榴石|鎂鐵榴石]]、[[尖晶橄欖石|尖晶橄欖石]]、[[重矽石|重矽石]]、[[β橄欖石|β橄欖石]]）<ref name="Coleman 1977">{{cite journal|last=Coleman|first=Leslie C.|title=Ringwoodite and majorite in the Catherwood meteorite|journal=Candadian Mineralogist|year=1977|volume=15|pages=97–101|url=http://canmin.geoscienceworld.org/content/15/1/97.extract|accessdate=19 December 2012|archive-date=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506194459/http://canmin.geoscienceworld.org/content/15/1/97.extract|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ohtani 2010">{{cite journal|last=Ohtani|first=E.|author2=Ozawa, S. |author3=Miyahara, M. |author4=Ito, Y. |author5=Mikouchi, T. |author6=Kimura, M. |author7=Arai, T. |author8=Sato, K. |author9= Hiraga, K. |displayauthors=9 |title=Coesite and stishovite in a shocked lunar meteorite, Asuka-881757, and impact events in lunar surface|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|date=27 December 2010|volume=108|issue=2|pages=463–466|doi=10.1073/pnas.1009338108|bibcode = 2011PNAS..108..463O }}</ref><ref name="Ferroir 2008">{{cite journal|last=Ferroir|first=Tristan|author2=Beck, Pierre; Van de Moortèle, Bertrand; Bohn, Marcel; Reynard, Bruno; Simionovici, Alexandre; El Goresy, Ahmed; Gillet, Philippe|title=Akimotoite in the Tenham meteorite: Crystal chemistry and high-pressure transformation mechanisms|journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters|date=1 October 2008|volume=275|issue=1–2|pages=26–31|doi=10.1016/j.epsl.2008.07.048|bibcode = 2008E&PSL.275...26F |last3=Van De Moortèle|first3=Bertrand|last4=Bohn|first4=Marcel|last5=Reynard|first5=Bruno|last6=Simionovici|first6=Alexandre|last7=El Goresy|first7=Ahmed|last8=Gillet|first8=Philippe}}</ref>。水合礦物（例如[[黏土礦物|黏土礦物]]）是母體有液體活動的指標<ref name="Hutchison 1987">{{cite journal|last=Hutchison|first=R.|author2=Alexander, C.M.O. |author3=barber, D.J. |title=The Semarkona meteorite: First recorded occurrence of smectite in an ordinary chondrite, and its implications|journal=Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta|date=30 June 1987|volume=51|issue=7|pages=1875–1882|doi=10.1016/0016-7037(87)90178-5|bibcode = 1987GeCoA..51.1875H }}</ref>。

=== 放射性定年法 ===
輻射的方法可以定出隕石歷史階段的不同日期。來自[[太陽星雲|太陽星雲]]濃縮體會紀錄下[[富含鈣鋁|富含鈣鋁]]和[[隕石球粒|隕石球粒]]。這些可以利用太陽星雲的放射性元素定年（例如[[鋁|<sup>26</sup>鋁/<sup>26</sup>鎂]]、[[錳|<sup>53</sup>錳/<sup>53</sup>鉻]]、[[鉛-鉛定年|鈾/鉛]]、[[碘|<sup>129</sup>碘/<sup>129</sup>氙]]）。在這些凝聚物達到[[微星|微星]]的尺度之後，就會發生融化和分異。這些過程可以利用[[鉛-鉛定年|鈾/鉛]]、[[銣-鍶定年|<sup>87</sup>銣/<sup>87</sup>鍶]]<ref name="Birck 1978">{{cite journal|last=Birck|first=J.L.|author2=Allègre, C.J.|title=Chronology and chemical history of the parent body of basaltic achondrites studied by the 87Rb-87Sr method|journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters|date=28 February 1978|volume=39|issue=1|pages=37–51|doi=10.1016/0012-821X(78)90139-5|bibcode = 1978E&PSL..39...37B }}</ref>、[[釤-釹定年|<sup>147</sup>釤/<sup>143</sup>釹]]和[[鑥-鉿定年|<sup>176</sup>鑥/<sup>176</sup>鉿]]法<ref name="Bouvier 2008">{{cite journal|last=Bouvier|first=Audrey|author2=Vervoort, Jeffrey D. |author3=Patchett, P. Jonathan |title=The Lu–Hf and Sm–Nd isotopic composition of CHUR: Constraints from unequilibrated chondrites and implications for the bulk composition of terrestrial planets|journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters|date=31 July 2008|volume=273|issue=1–2|pages=48–57|doi=10.1016/j.epsl.2008.06.010|bibcode = 2008E&PSL.273...48B }}</ref>。金屬核心的形成和冷凝可以用[[錸鋨定年|<sup>187</sup>錸/<sup>187</sup>鋨法]]追溯應用在[[鐵隕石|鐵隕石]]<ref name="Smoliar 1996">{{cite journal|last=Smoliar|first=M. I.|author2=Walker, R. J. |author3=Morgan, J. W. |title=Re-Os Ages of Group IIA, IIIA, IVA, and IVB Iron Meteorites|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_science_1996-02-23_271_5252/page/1099|journal=Science|date=23 February 1996|volume=271|issue=5252|pages=1099–1102|doi=10.1126/science.271.5252.1099|bibcode = 1996Sci...271.1099S }}</ref><ref name="Report about Smolar 1996">{{cite web|title=Re-Os ages of group IIA, IIIA, IVA, and IVB iron from meteorites.|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-18089497.html|accessdate=19 December 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413133001/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-18089497.html|archive-date=2016-04-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。大型撞擊事件，或甚至導致母體銷毀可以利用[[氬-氬定年|<sup>39</sup>氬 /<sup>40</sup>氬法]]和[[分裂痕跡定年法|<sup>244</sup>鈽分裂痕跡法]]<ref name="Bogard 1990">{{cite journal|last=Bogard|first=D.D|author2=Garrison, D.H |author3=Jordan, auJ.L |author4= Mittlefehldt, D |title=39Ar-40Ar dating of mesosiderites: Evidence for major parent body disruption < 4 Ga ago|journal=Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta|date=31 August 1990|volume=54|issue=9|pages=2549–2564|doi=10.1016/0016-7037(90)90241-C|bibcode = 1990GeCoA..54.2549B }}</ref>。在與母體分離後，流星體都暴露在宇宙輻射中。這段時期的長短可以使用[[氚氦定年|<sup>3</sup>氚/<sup>3</sup>氦]]、[[鈉氖定年|<sup>22</sup>鈉/<sup>21</sup>氖]]、[[氪氪定年|<sup>81</sup>氪 /<sup>83</sup>氪]]<ref name="Eugster 1988">{{cite journal|last=Eugster|first=O|title=Cosmic-ray production rates for 3He, 21Ne, 38Ar, 83Kr, and 126Xe in chondrites based on 81Kr-Kr exposure ages|journal=Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta|date=31 May 1988|volume=52|issue=6|pages=1649–1662|doi=10.1016/0016-7037(88)90233-5|bibcode = 1988GeCoA..52.1649E }}</ref><ref name="Nishiizumi 1980">{{cite journal|last=Nishiizumi|first=K.|author2=Regnier, S. |author3=Marti, K. |title=Cosmic ray exposure ages of chondrites, pre-irradiation and constancy of cosmic ray flux in the past|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_earth-and-planetary-science-letters_1980-10_50_1/page/156|journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters|date=1 October 1980|volume=50|issue=1|pages=156–170|doi=10.1016/0012-821X(80)90126-0|bibcode = 1980E&PSL..50..156N }}</ref>。在撞擊到地球之後
（或任何其他足以遮蔽掉宇宙射線的行星），肇因於宇宙射線的核衰變可以用來定出墜落的時間。暴露在地球上的時間是用[[氯|<sup>36</sup>氯]]、[[放射性碳定年法|<sup>14</sup>碳]]、[[氪|<sup>81</sup>氪]]<ref name="Nishiizumi 1989">{{cite journal|last=Nishiizumi|first=K.|author2=Elmore, D. |author3=Kubik, P.W. |title=Update on terrestrial ages of Antarctic meteorites|journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters|date=30 June 1989|volume=93|issue=3–4|pages=299–313|doi=10.1016/0012-821X(89)90029-0|bibcode = 1989E&PSL..93..299N }}</ref>。

